-[wes] how much money?

03:58.906 --> 04:00.606
So $2.5 million.

04:01.408 --> 04:03.408
$2.5 million in sales in that
product.

04:03.977 --> 04:06.811
And then you said another 300,
so you've got another--

04:06.814 --> 04:08.546
$1.6 million.

04:08.549 --> 04:10.749
So about $4.1 million in sales
next year projected?

04:10.751 --> 04:12.517
Correct.

04:13.721 --> 04:15.921
How much of that that you're
gonna have in the bank?

04:16.857 --> 04:18.824
I think we will definitely bank
over half of it.

04:19.826 --> 04:21.793
So you think you're gonna make
$2 million of profit?

04:21.861 --> 04:23.695
-Correct.
-Wow.

04:23.763 --> 04:24.963
[arlene] so why are you here?

04:24.965 --> 04:28.967
Right now, I do not have enough
capital to be able to meet

04:29.036 --> 04:30.301
